{
  "stem": "27390.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Then they  were-- we were told to stand to attention.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And a lot of SS came along, and they picked out 131 boys.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I was lucky to be-- well my brother was picked out, but I , I ran across.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they were picked out, they were standing about 10 yards from, from us, these boys that were picked out to work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We guessed they were taken to work because they picked the healthier boys.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So I just took a chance and I ran across as they were standing there with the dogs and they were busy looking and talking to each other.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I took-- I had nothing to lose.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I just-- you, you learn by instinct.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "In such situations, it's a split-second decision you have to make.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I ran across.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "If I will be caught, they would have shot me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I managed to get across.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I was together with my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And then we were taken to a place, into another barrack, where we were given tattoos on the arms.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "You see, if you managed to get that tattoo in-- in Auschwitz you were safe for, for the time being you were safe.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Without the tattoo, you were destined to, to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "If you had that tattoo, that meant that you were going to be sent to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Didn't know how long he would be able to, to, to survive at work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But at least you weren't taken right away to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were given the, the tattoos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were taken out from this camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were taken into another camp, where we were put in quarantine for three weeks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this camp was-- they had-- it was a show camp because we had proper bunks.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
